    <p>
        Learning point
    </p>
    <p>
        <ul>
            <li>
                <p>
                    Flipping a coin or tossing a dice are examples of chance experiments.
                </p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>
                    A trial or chance experiment may have different possible outcomes.
                </p>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </p>
